images.title: A holiday tradition endures
images.caption: Dancing in 'The Nutcracker'
images.desc: If it's December, then countless dance companies are likely performing 'The Nutcracker.' The ballet has become an iconic holiday entertainment staple, produced around the world. This photo captures a scene from the 2016 production by the English National Ballet at the London Coliseum. The company has been performing 'The Nutcracker' during the Christmas season since 1950.
